# Custom Page Section Compatibility Spec

## Scope

Frozen input, rendering, edit, copy, duplicate, and live-update behavior that the
typed page-section migration must preserve. This is a compatibility baseline,
not authorization to keep the legacy document model after cutover.

## Load when

Changing `pages.content`, page section/item types, `BlockRenderer`, section
toolbars, registry validation, saved custom sections, page duplication, or page
WebSocket reconciliation.

